{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-markdown-remark-js","path":"/hitchhikers-guide/sre/sli-slo/tools.md","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Operate First"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"fc0bfc71-d55e-5e36-af7d-3028bd5c0b51","html":"<p>This page highlights the operational tools and services monitored through Operate First.</p>\n<h2 id=\"operational-tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#operational-tools\" aria-label=\"operational tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Operational Tools</h2>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://prometheus.io/\">Prometheus</a> - Monitoring tool capturing time series metrics for available Operate First services</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://prometheus.io/docs/alerting/latest/alertmanager/\">Prometheus Alertmanager</a> - Alertmanager for handling alerts and routing them to the appropriate receiver integration such as Email, Slack, PagerDuty etc</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://grafana.com/\">Grafana</a> - Visualization tool for creating monitoring dashboards</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/m-lab/alertmanager-github-receiver\">GitHub Receiver</a> - Incident reporting tool for handling outages/incidents</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"services-monitored\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#services-monitored\" aria-label=\"services monitored permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Services Monitored</h2>\n<p>We have <a href=\"https://opendatahub.io/\">Open Data Hub</a> applications deployed and running in a MOC <a href=\"https://massopen.cloud/\">(Mass Open Cloud)</a> cluster. Open Data Hub is an end-to-end AI/ML platform on top of OpenShift Container Platform which provides various tools for Data Scientists and Engineers.</p>\n<p>The components we currently have available are:</p>\n<ul class=\"pf-c-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https://jupyterhub-opf-jupyterhub.apps.smaug.na.operate-first.cloud/login\">JupyterHub</a>: which hosts interactive Jupyter notebooks. You can see the runbook for how to administer SRE practices on JupyterHub <a href=\"https://www.operate-first.cloud/users/sre/runbooks/jupyterhub.md\">here</a>.</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"srcLink":"https://github.com/operate-first/SRE/blob/master/sli-slo/tools.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"","description":null,"extraClasses":null,"banner":null}}},"pageContext":{"id":"fc0bfc71-d55e-5e36-af7d-3028bd5c0b51"}},"staticQueryHashes":["117426894","1764348645","3000541721","3606484676"]}